sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 用户(小程序)
    participant API as NestJS API
    participant RecSvc as RecommendService
    participant WthSvc as WeatherService
    participant VRepo as VenueRepository
    participant Cache as Redis Cache
    participant QWeather as 和风天气API

    Note over User, QWeather: 核心流程：用户获取Top3推荐

    User->>API: GET /api/v1/recommend/top3?ageGroup=1-3&budgetLevel=economy
    API->>RecSvc: getTop3({ ageGroup, budgetLevel })

    RecSvc->>WthSvc: getWeekendWeather("上海")
    WthSvc->>Cache: 查询天气缓存
    alt 缓存命中
        Cache-->>WthSvc: 返回缓存天气数据
    else 缓存未命中
        WthSvc->>QWeather: 请求上海3天天气预报
        QWeather-->>WthSvc: 返回天气数据
        WthSvc->>Cache: 写入缓存(TTL=30min)
    end
    WthSvc-->>RecSvc: { condition: "sunny", tempHigh: 28, recommendation: "outdoor" }

    RecSvc->>Cache: 查询推荐结果缓存(key=ageGroup+budget+weather)
    alt 缓存命中
        Cache-->>RecSvc: 返回缓存推荐结果
    else 缓存未命中
        RecSvc->>RecSvc: 执行三维筛选策略
        Note over RecSvc: 1. weatherStrategy: 晴天→户外70%+室内30%
        Note over RecSvc: 2. ageStrategy: 1-3岁→过滤minAge>36月, bestAge加权
        Note over RecSvc: 3. budgetStrategy: economy→avgCost<=100

        RecSvc->>VRepo: findByFilter(weather, age, budget)
        VRepo-->>RecSvc: 候选场所列表(按compositeScore排序)

        RecSvc->>RecSvc: 取Top5，选取差异度最大的3个方案
        RecSvc->>RecSvc: 生成优劣势分析
        RecSvc->>RecSvc: 选择天气备选方案

        RecSvc->>Cache: 写入推荐结果缓存(TTL=1h)
    end

    RecSvc-->>API: RecommendResult
    API-->>User: { code: 0, data: { plans: [A, B, C], backupPlan, weather } }

    Note over User, QWeather: 用户查看方案详情

    User->>API: GET /api/v1/venues/:venueId
    API->>VRepo: findById(venueId)
    VRepo-->>API: 场所详情+评价+预约链接
    API-->>User: { code: 0, data: venueDetail }

    Note over User, QWeather: 用户点击预约跳转

    User->>API: POST /api/v1/booking/click { venueId, platform }
    API-->>User: { code: 0, data: { recorded: true } }
    User->>User: 跳转到大众点评小程序/H5/拨号
